&lt;li&gt;Competency with AI tools (e.g., ChatGPT, Claude, Copilot) for tasks like drafting, research and automation; willingness to explore how AI can accelerate solution design and customer delivery&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clear and confident communication skills in English (written and spoken); additional European languages are a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactive, collaborative attitude - you ask questions, take initiative, and don&#39;t wait to be told what to do&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willingness to travel occasionally (up to 25% out of term time)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;First experience in manufacturing is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
